#\#CIF_2.0
# Tests: powder diffractogram structured table routing with a small dataset.
# _pd_meas.2theta_scan and _pd_meas.intensity_total are routed to the pd_meas table.
# _pd_diffractogram.id provides the diffractogram_id context for the FK.
#
# There is no key tag given in the loop. A UUID value is assigned per row, and
# is assigned to _pd_meas.point_id, _pd_proc.point_id, as well as _pd_data.point.id.
#
# Dictionary: cif_pow

data_test_small_pd_meas_calc
_diffrn_radiation.id    lab_tube
_diffrn_radiation.probe x-ray
_pd_diffractogram.id    test_scan
loop_
  _pd_meas.2theta_scan
  _pd_meas.intensity_total
  _pd_calc.intensity_total
  10.000  100.0 101.3
  10.100  120.0 121.3
  10.200  110.0 123.4
  10.300   95.0  96.3
  10.400  105.0 104.3
